</ul>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#1e889b">#include</span> <span style="color:#1e889b">&lt;array&gt;</span><span style="color:#1e889b">
